
1  Ore ake pee ekenyu, neiguana ilapolosak kituaak, o lpayiani o lasirak o enkiguana pooki nalulung'a. Neen Yesu, nerik neitarasaki Pilato. 
2  Neikilikuan Pilato ajoki, “Ira doi iyie Olaiguanani loo Lyahudi?” Newaliki ajoki, “Iyie otejo neijia.” 
3  Neitang'or ilapolosak kituaak ninye too mbaa kumok. 
4  Neigil Pilato aikilikuan ninye ajoki, “Aimiata hoo embae niwalu? Nidol eneba mbaa nikintang'orie ninche?” 
5  Kake eitu hoo ewaliki Yesu, metaba anaa neing'asia Pilato.


6  Naa ore apake te ilo sirua kelaaki apa ninye ninche oltung'ani obo oena, naa olotoomonutuo ake. 
7  Ore too ltung'ana oopidilare enkitoria ooena te korokoroni, neitayutuo loikop ina kata, netii oltung'ani oji Barabas. 
8  Nelotu ina siamo neiter aaikilikuan Pilato meitaasa enoshi ake naitaas. 
9  Newaliki ajoki, “Iyieuu nalaaki intae Olaiguanani loo Lyahudi?” 
10  Amu etayiolo Pilato ajo olom ake eitarasarie ilapolosak kituaak Yesu. 
11  Kake einuaakita ilapolosak kituaak olorere metejo pee elaakini ninche Barabas. 
12  Neitoki ake Pilato ajoki ninche, “Paa kaa naa aitaas ele tung'ani lijojo Olaiguanani loo Lyahudi?” 
13  Neilepilep aaigil aajo, “Tasho ninye.” 
14  Nejoki Pilato ninche, “Ainyoo, kaa torrono etaasa ninye?” Kake eilepilepa oleng aajo, “Tasho ninye.” 
15  Ore amu keyieu Pilato neitiship ina siamo, nelaaki Barabas neng'as aishooyo Yesu metooshi too nkeenta neitoki aitarasaa metashei.

