16  Neriku sikarini ninye atua enkaji e nkitoo naji praitorio; neipotu esikari e sirit nalulung'a. 
17  Neishopoki ninye olkila mugie neshetu olmarisian loo lkiku neishopoki Yesu elukunya. 
18  Neiter aairoroki aajoki, “Olele Olaiguanani loo Lyahudi!” 
19  Neigilie aaosh elukunya te ntiyani, nenotaki, negilaki kung aaitaakuno keserem. 
20  Ore pee eidip aatadalare, neoru ilo kila mugie neishopoki nkilani enyena. Nerik auluo pee epuo aashe.

