33  Ore pee eipir enkolong, nerip enaimin enkop pooki o metabaiki saa naaudo. 
34   Ore pee eaku saa naaudo nebuak Yesu to ltoilo sapuk ajo, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?” eji, “Enkai ai, Enkai ai, ainyoo pee kitung'uayie?” 
35  Ore pee ening kulikae ooitashe te ine nejo, “Ining, Eliya eipoto.” 
36   Nekuet obo, neiput osuguroi enaisho naisuisho naji siki, nepik oloomi neisho metooko, ejo, “Ntasho matodol te naa kelotu Eliya aitadou.” 
37  Nebuaku Yesu oleng, nedung'o tau. 
38   Neiperra aaku are olkarasha oor enkaji e Nkai, eiteru te shumata o meiting'o ti abori. 
39  Ore pee edol osajini oitashe aipirare ninye, ajo etaa etundung'e tau, nejo, “Edede Oinoti le Nkai ele tung'ani.”


40   Netii sii nkituaak naaing'orita elakuaniki inaatii Mariamu Magdalene, o Mariamu ng'otonye Yakobo oti o Yosef, netii sii Salome, 
41  ninche napa, etii ninye Galilaya, naatusujutua neisiaai. Netii sii kulie kituaak kumok naairiamunore ninye epuonu Yerusalem.

