42  Ore pee eaku teipa, naa enkolong e Nkitobirakinoto, aa enoshi olong taa pee eyookini enkolong e nkiyeng'iyeng'ata. 
43  Neshirraki Yosef le Arimatea, obo loo looyanyiti le nkiguana, olaa keanyita ninye enkitoria e Nkai, nelo enetii Pilato neomonu osesen le Yesu. 
44  Neing'asia Pilato pee eji eidipa Yesu atua, ore pee eipotu osajini, neikilikuan te naa keidipa atua. 
45  Ore pee ening to sajini ajo etua, neisho Yosef ilo sesen. 
46  Neinyang'u ninye olkarasha le kitani, neirragie te nkurare nataguetuaki to soit, neibeleleng'oki osoit enkutuk e ina kurare. 
47  Netoduaa Mariamu Magdalene o Mariamu ng'otonye Yosef eneirragieki ninye.

